article:
List of the 'National Register of Historic Places listings in Manhattan from
59th to 110th Streets'


This is intended to be a complete list of properties and districts listed on the
National Register of Historic Places between 59th and 110th Streets in
Manhattan. For properties and districts in other parts of Manhattan and the
other islands of New York County, see National Register of Historic Places
listings in New York County, New York. The locations of National Register
properties and districts (at least for all showing latitude and longitude
coordinates below) may be seen in a Google map by clicking on "Map of all
coordinates".
